{"id": "1197514822930153563", "channel_id": "1197514822930153563", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "刚刚突然看见+12ssr后再度抽到重复资源只能获得150沉淀，经过一番思考后我觉得这个会很大的影响到我抽卡的心情。\n如图所示，在下版本补偿5回溯后我能很轻松的将我最喜欢的角色+12。\n以后在抽池子时抽到重复的只能获得150沉淀的补偿，又因为我每个月都会给游戏充一笔钱导致每月沉淀商店中真正有用的资源都会被清空。\n这样给的150沉淀会在很长的时间中不能转化为我需要的资源，这样很大程度会降低我抽卡的动力。\n建议官方将150沉淀换成重复2-3次后获得一个自选，又或者能掉落刷新商店的道具，让我将资源变现。\n\n官方好好照顾下氪金玩家吧，优化下这些边边角角的体验，让我们能放心氪金呀。\n\n我连没啥用的钥令 不平等交换都买了，现在这些沉淀是比较溢出的，体验真的很差。", "timestamp": "2024-01-18T12:16:22.536000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-18T12:19:01.316000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1197514823974526976", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-02-55-337_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 127237, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197514822930153563/1197514823974526976/Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-02-55-337_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a007716&is=69ff2596&hm=10ff2413de0f677547b2cfe3492948076e2143a7190725038476a768c1327b8e&"}, {"id": "1197514824490434611", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-06-15-517_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 186490, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197514822930153563/1197514824490434611/Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-06-15-517_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a007716&is=69ff2596&hm=21b24f217f012d757b96c8aafb16bcbe1a157619f2abfe61e49ba715d40f9189&"}, {"id": "1197514824964382760", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-05-59-779_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 192420, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197514822930153563/1197514824964382760/Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-05-59-779_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a007717&is=69ff2597&hm=69f8657d0a9ee3ed8f0d7aa42aebefabeeee28c11ff2fb566b76ca850540b68f&"}, {"id": "1197514825543200828", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-18-20-